# No More Last Minute: A Smart Study Planner with Mood & Productivity Tracking

**No More Last Minute** is designed to help students manage their academic tasks, track their study habits, and improve productivity in a simple and effective way. It integrates task management, mood tracking, and study time analysis into one platform to support better study planning.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

